title: No More Heroes OST - Dark Side
description:
More music from the videogame No More Heroes.

Actually I don't think any of these were actually in the game, but they are remixes or covers of certain songs that were.

Tracks:
1. It's Kill Or Be Killed Mix
2. N.M.H. 6955 Mix
3. NO MORE RIOT
4. PURE WHITE GIANT TINY GLASTONBURY
5. Hustlin' 'n' Tusslin' [Batucafro Mix]
6. N.M.H. The Outer Rim Remix
7. We Are Finally Cowboys [Golden Brown Mix]
8. ANY MORE (RX-Ver.S.P.L.)
9. The Virgin Child Makes Her Wish Without Feeling Anything [Ver.V]
